* Episodes 28—35 premiered exclusively in the United States via Amazon Prime Video on April 23 , 2018 .
* Episodes 15—37 were confirmed when rumours about the series ' hiatus were released in the press in August 2017 .
The production team have since stated that two further episodes were shot in the autumn , bringing the total number of episodes to 39 .
An insider told The Herald ; " Twenty - three episodes for next year are already shot and in the can .
But what is n't generally known is that two more episodes are being made which will be shot late this year . "
